text.section:
The Fund consists of:
Any money received under this title for:
Commercial licenses and permits;
Service fees, taxes, and royalties paid to the State for oyster shells and clam shells removed from the bottom beneath the tidal waters of the State;
The sale of seed oysters under § 4-1103 of this title; and
Any fine or forfeiture collected under § 4-1202 of this title;
Any investment earnings of the Fund;
Money received from any other source; and
Money appropriated from the General Fund of the State in accordance with subsection (j) of this section.
